data.title: 准备以至少20秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: Let me talk about someone who is notorious. Tim is someone notorious that I know of in my high school because he drove illegally and challenged the police. He drove exceeding the limit of speed, and when a police officer notified him and chased him, he rejected to slow down. Instead, he even increased his speed to try to get rid of the police officer. He got punished after for a $2000 penalty and everyone in my high school knows him because of this.
data.referenceText: Talk about someone notorious that you know of. What makes them notorious？
data.referenceTranslate: 说说你知道的某个臭名昭著的人。是什么让他们声名狼藉？
